024 / 2:30 AM EDT\n\n108\n\nSquare Enix expects to recognize extraordinary losses of 22.1 billion yen in\n\u201ccontent abandonment losses\u201d for the fiscal year ended March 2024, the company\nannounced.\n\nThe Board of Directors voted to \u201crevise the Group\u2019s approach to the\ndevelopment of high-definition (HD) games with the intention of being more\nselective and focused in the allocation of development resources.\u201d The losses\nare a result of this revised approach.\n\nGet the full announcement below.\n\n> \u25a0 Notification of Recognition of Extraordinary Losses\n>\n> Square Enix Holdings Co., Ltd. expects to recognize extraordinary losses\n> pertaining to abandonment losses associated with its content production\n> account on its books for the fiscal year ended March 2024, as detailed\n> below.\n>\n> 1\\. Nature of the Extraordinary Losses\n>\n> At the meeting convened on March 27, 2024, the Board of Directors of Square\n> Enix Holdings Co., Ltd. (the \u201cCompany\u201d) voted, in light of the myriad\n> changes underway in the environment surrounding its Group, to revise the\n> Group\u2019s approach to the development of high-definition (HD) games with the\n> intention of being more selective and focused in the allocation of\n> development resources. As a result of a close examination of the Group\u2019s\n> development pipeline undertaken in keeping with this revised approach, the\n> Company expects to recognize approximately \u00a522.1 billion in content\n> abandonment losses on its books for the fiscal year ended March 2024.\n>\n> 2\\. Outlook\n>\n> The Company is carefully reviewing its consolidated forecasts for the fiscal\n> year ended March 2024 to assess the potential for impact from the above or\n> other factors. Should revisions to its forecasts prove necessary, the\n> Company will promptly disclose the same.\n\nCompany Profile\n\n## Square Enix\n\n#### Upcoming Events View all\n\n  * ##### Tokyo Game Dungeon 5\n\nMay 3 @ 11:00 pm - May 4 @ 4:00 am EDT\n\n  * ##### INDIE Live Expo 2024\n\nMay 24 - May 25\n\n  * ##### IGN Live 2024\n\nJune 7 - June 10\n\n  * ##### Summer Game Fest 2024 Showcase\n\nJune 7 @ 5:00 pm - 6:30 pm EDT\n\n### What\u2019s Popular\n\n###### Square Enix to record extraordinary loss of 22.1 billion yen in\n\u201ccontent abandonment losses\u201d following revised development approach\n\n###### Vampire Survivors version 1.10 \u2018Laborratory\u2019 update now available\n\n###### Sci-fi 2.5D adventure RPG Beyond Galaxyland announced for PS5, Xbox\nSeries, PS4, Xbox One, Switch, and PC\n\n###### Dragon Ball: Sparking! ZERO \u2018Master and Apprentice\u2019 trailer,\nscreenshots\n\n### Recent Comments\n\n###### Sendaimon \u00bb Open Forum #344\n\n50 seconds ago\n\n###### Lulu \u00bb Genso Manege coming west for Switch, PC\n\n5 minutes ago\n\n###### Zhu \u00bb Square Enix to record extraordinary loss of 22.1 billion yen in\n\u201ccontent abandonment losses\u201d following revised development approach\n\n5 minutes ago\n\n###### Zhu \u00bb Square Enix to record extraordinary loss of 22.1 billion yen in\n\u201ccontent abandonment losses\u201d following revised development approach\n\n7 minutes ago\n\nLatest Open Forum \u00bb\n\n### Related Content\n\n  * Smartphone\n  * Switch\n\n3 hours ago1\n\n#### Star Wars: Hunters launches June 4\n\n  * PC\n  * PS4\n  * PS5\n  * Switch\n  * Xbox One\n  * Xbox Series\n\n3 hours ago1\n\n#### Shin Megami Tensei V: Vengeance \u2018An Ideal World\u2019 trailer\n\n  * PC\n  * Switch\n\n4 hours ago2\n\n#### Genso Manege coming west for Switch, PC\n\n  * PC\n  * PS5\n  * Switch\n  * Xbox Series\n\n5 hours ago2\n\n#### The Land Beneath Us launches May 13\n\n### Comments\n\n\u00a9 Copyright Gematsu 2008 to 2023. All rights reserved.\n\nReproduction in whole or in part in any form or medium without acknowledgment\nof Gematsu is prohibited. Use of this site is governed by all applicable laws.\n\nWebsite by 44 Bytes\n\n", "frontpage": true}
